titleInfo.title: Four-loop singlet contribution to the electroweak rho parameter

mods.abstract: We compute the four-loop QCD contribution to the electroweak rho parameter induced by the singlet diagrams of the Z-boson self-energy. The numerical impact on the weak mixing angle and the W-boson mass is small. (c) 2005 Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.
